data.description: This remarkable home has all the feelings of country home with all natural woodwork, hardwood floors, a country look kitchen and a very large back yard with a pergola. There is a first floor den, office, playroom etc with a gas burning stove, a formal dining room and a beautiful foyer with wood staircase leading to the upstairs four bedrooms. Included is a finished bedroom on the third floor which would make for another playroom etc.
